    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458881>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458883>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458885>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458887> ;
