<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458881>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Distribution map with pictures of live specimens. A. Sphaerobelum cattiense sp. nov.; B. Sphaerobelum konkakinhense sp. nov.; C. Zephronia konkakinhensis sp. nov.; D. Zephronia montis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458881/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458883>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Sphaerobelum cattiense sp. nov. A–G = male paratypes, I = female paratype (all ZMUM). A. left anterior telopod, anterior view; B. left anterior telopod, lateral view; C. left anterior telopod, posterior view; D. leg 9, right, anterior view; E. right posterior telopod, posterior view; F. right posterior telopod, anterior view; G. telopoditomere 4, lateral view; H. right male antenna; I. left coxa and prefemur with vulva. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458883/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458885>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Sphaerobelum cattiense sp. nov. Male paratype (ZFMK MYR6516), right antenna. A. lateral view; B. apical view of disc; C. details of apical cone. Abbreviations: sc = sclerotized scales; sb = sensilla basiconica. Scale bars: A = 1000 µm; B = 200 µm; C = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458885/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458887>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Endoterga of midbody rings. A. Sphaerobelum cattiense sp. nov. Male paratype (ZFMK MYR6516); B. Sphaerobelum konkakinhense sp. nov., male holotype (ZMUM). Scale bars: 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

